	loading_magma = "Battlemaster Pugna draws great pleasure in subjecting combatants to the whims of his Battlearena forged of stone and fire.",
	loading_magma2 = "To escape the fiery Forge, our Survivors must triumph in battle against Battlemaster Pugna's fearsome champions.",
	loading_maxwell = "Maxwell's extended reign on the Nightmare Throne altered him in ways that are not yet fully understood. He continues to rely heavily on his tome, the Codex Umbra, as a result.",
