	loading_pigking = "Legend has it the Pig King and his followers left their home long ago to rule freely in The Constant.",
	loading_webber = "Webber could have easily seen his unique predicament as an affliction or a curse. Instead, he's chosen to view it as a second chance, and one that he fully intends not to waste.",
	loading_webber_feast = "\"We're super excited to watch everyone open the presents we got them.\"",
	loading_wendy = "Wendy clings fiercely to the grief over her sister's death, for fear that moving on would cause Abigail's memory to fade.",
	loading_wendy_creepy = "She can't escape her monomaniacal obsession with death.\nNeither can you.",
	loading_wendy_victorian = "Wendy finds a strange comfort in elaborate mourning rituals.\nIt takes the guesswork out of grieving.",
	loading_wes_victorian = "There are few more satisfying feelings in life than knowing one's work is done for the day.",
	loading_wickerbottom = "Delightfully, Ms. Wickerbottom has found her passion for the written word has only deepened as the years go by. Any knowledge committed to paper becomes impervious to the brain fogs of age, you know!",
	loading_wickerbottom_victorian = "It's a well-known fact that a group of crows is called a \"murder\".\nIt is a lesser known fact that they hold crow funerals.",
	loading_wigfrid = "The valor and confidence of a Valkyrie didn't always come naturally to Wigfrid. She cultivated her strength and persona over many years through sheer force of will.",
